ch.gbssg.core

Interface IFilterEntity<T extends AbsModel>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of entity. It must be extension of a ICommand
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    User

    public interface IFilterEntity<T extends AbsModel>
    Represent a filter for database entities. You can send a IFilterEntity to the DatabaseController via CmdFilterEntity. So, the ICrud Interface returns all merged entities of the database collection.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pedrett Sandro
